{{refimprove|date=October 2018}} {{Use dmy dates|date=May 2014}} {{Infobox recurring event | name = drupa | native_name = | logo = [[File:drupa logo.jpg|150px]] | logo_caption = | image = | imagesize = | caption = | date = <!--"dates=" also works, as merged from Template:Infobox festival. Do not use both--> | begins = 2020-06-16 | ends = 2020-06-26 | frequency = [[wikt:quadrennial|Every 4 years]] | venue = Düsseldorf Fairgrounds | location = [[Düsseldorf]], [[North Rhine-Westphalia]], [[Germany]] | years_active = | first = {{Start date|df=yes|1951}} | last = <!--2016--> | participants = 1828 from 54 countries (2016) | attendance = 260,165 from 183 countries (2016) | genre = Printing equipment | budget = | patron = | organised = [[Messe Düsseldorf]] | website = {{URL|http://www.drupa.com}} | footnotes = <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.drupa.com/cipp/md_drupa/lib/pub/object/downloadfile,oid,30748/lang,2/ticket,g_u_e_s_t/~/tradefairprofile_2012.pdf |title=drupa 2012 Profile |publisher=[[Messe Düsseldorf]] |accessdate=17 August 2014}}</ref> }}
The '''drupa''' is the largest [[printing]] equipment exhibition in the world, held every four years by [[Messe Düsseldorf]] in Düsseldorf, North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany. The word drupa is a [[portmanteau]] of the German words '''dru'''ck und '''pa'''pier; ''print'' and ''paper'' respectively.
Thousands of industry experts are usually present, and corporate representation typically includes companies such as [[Agfa-Gevaert|Agfa Graphics]], [[Océ|Océ N.V.]], [[Muller Martini]], [[EIZO (Eizo Nanao Corporation)|EIZO]], [[Esko (company)|Esko]], [[Hewlett-Packard]], [[Xeikon]], [[Flint Group]], [[Heidelberger Druckmaschinen]], [[Manroland]], Kern, [[Pitney Bowes]], New Solution, [[Xerox]], [[Kodak]], [[Canon (company)|Canon]], [[Transeomedia]], [[DirectSmile]], [[Konica Minolta]], [[Ricoh]], Martin Automatic, [[Komori Corporation]], [[Fujifilm]], [[Siegwerk]], [[Inspectron]] and [[Koenig & Bauer AG]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.drupa.com/cgi-bin/md_drupa/vis/custom/ext2/download.cgi/drupa12.html?ticket=k-U2FsdGVkX18_oeQGWmm6hQ8t2nh20pcKul9JDbh0whQ&dl=html |title=drupa 2012 Exhibitors |publisher=[[Messe Düsseldorf]] |accessdate=17 August 2014}}</ref> Several new technologies are typically demonstrated during Drupa.
